body_html:
Hi mrry,
Thank you very much for your help. I have rebuilt and I have been able to generate the tensorflow.dll.
I have run the model resnet vs inception (trained with my own dataset) in a machine with card graphic GForce 1080Ti. The times measured to detect objects are below:

  • CPU ~ 27.8 sec
  • GPU ~ 6.79 sec

I can see with GPU enabled it works better, but still is not enough. Could you tell me please if there is any make it faster?

Thank you again for all help provided.
